MTA utils (1.3-1)

  * Fix key buffer overrun by using additional call to EVP_EncryptInit_ex to set the key
  * size after initial call to EVP_EncryptInit_ex which set the algorithm only
  -- Gavriel Karasin <gavrielk@mta.ac.il>  Sun, 10 Jan 2021 22:25:00 +0300
 
MTA utils (1.2-1)

  * Replace AES-256-ECB with RC2-ECB encryption algorithm to avoid key and data padding 
  * RC2-ECB supports any key size between 8-1024 as long as it is devidable by 8
  -- Gavriel Karasin <gavrielk@mta.ac.il>  Fri, 1 Jan 2021 20:47:00 +0300
  
